data.description: Prime location in the heart of Moss Bluff. Brick home located on a corner lot near the middle school. This house features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a kitchen that opens into the living area, covered Carport, laundry/bonus room is located off the carport with bathroom, a pecan tree. Laundry/Bonus room could be converted into a man cave or a outdoor kitchen, this room is not included in the living sq. ft.
